I have enough context to write the verifier. The implementation will stay path-strict: enumerate live Compound markets, try the exact `mint -> shortfall transfer-in -> excess cToken mint -> redeem` sequence only when the verifier actually holds a listed underlying, and otherwise record the concrete fork-state blocker that no listed market satisfies the fee-on-transfer precondition.
