+        /*
+            Fork-state blocker at block 18,759,540:
+            Compound's listed markets are the canonical cETH/cDAI/cBAT/cUSDC/cUSDT/cWBTC/cSAI/cREP/cZRX/cUNI/cCOMP/cLINK/cTUSD/cAAVE/cMKR/cSUSHI/cYFI/cWBTC2/cFEI set.
